page.title: 02A day in my life
page.content: When we come back we take the tack off and brush the sweat, off then we take them up the field.I do not feed mine because he is fat but Lisa feeds hers.I say goodbye to the family and cycle home.It takes me about 20 minutes to cycle home because it is all up hill.When I get home it is about 1.30 and it is time for dinner. After dinner I watch Sons and Daugters because it is very good.It is 4.00 and I go jogging with my mum.When we come back we take the dogs for a walk.When we come back I go inside and watch television.I watched Coronation Street and Dallas.After Dallas I go bed.I read for an hour and then go to sleep.
